<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bg">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Образованието е Бъдеще - Намери своята гимназия в София</title>
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f4f7f6 0%, #e0f2fe 100%);
            color: #333;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 950px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 1.2em 1.2em 1.2em;
        }

        section {
            padding: 1.5em 0 1.2em 0;
            margin-bottom: 1.2em;
            border-radius: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
            background: #fff;
            border: none;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
        }

            section:not(.hero):before {
                content: "";
                display: block;
                position: absolute;
                top: 0;
                left: 0;
                right: 0;
                height: 5px;
                background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ffa500 0%, #0056b3 100%);
                border-radius: 18px 18px 0 0;
                opacity: 0.15;
            }

            section:nth-of-type(even):not(.hero) {
                background: #fafdff;
            }

            section.hero {
                background: linear-gradient(120deg, #b3d4fc 0%, #e0f2fe 60%, #ffa500 100%), url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/cubes.png');
                background-blend-mode: lighten;
                color: #0056b3;
                box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,86,179,0.10);
                border: none;
                border-radius: 18px;
                position: relative;
                overflow: hidden;
            }

                section.hero::after {
                    content: "";
                    position: absolute;
                    inset: 0;
                    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
                    pointer-events: none;
                }

            section h3 {
                text-align: center;
                font-size: 2em;
                margin-bottom: 1.5em;
                color: #0056b3;
                letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            }

        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 2em;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .feature-item {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 2em 1.5em;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,86,179,0.07);
            border-left: 5px solid #ffa500;
            transition: box-shadow 0.2s, border-color 0.2s;
        }

            .feature-item:hover {
                box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0,86,179,0.13);
                border-left: 5px solid #0056b3;
            }

            .feature-item h4 {
                font-size: 1.3em;
                margin-bottom: 0.5em;
                color: #004a99;
            }

            .feature-item p {
                font-size: 1em;
                color: #555;
            }

        .about-snippet {
            background: #fff;
            border-top: 3px solid #b3d4fc;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #b3d4fc;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,86,179,0.04);
            border-radius: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 1.2em;
        }

            .about-snippet .container {
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                gap: 2em;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                padding: 0;
            }

            .about-snippet img.logo-placeholder {
                width: 100px;
                height: 100px;
                background-color: #ccc;
                border-radius: 50%;
                display: flex;
                align-items: center;
                justify-content: center;
                font-weight: bold;
                color: #fff;
            }

            .about-snippet p {
                flex-grow: 1;
                font-size: 1.1em;
                color: #444;
            }

        .about-project-snippet {
            background: #fafdff;
            border: 1px solid #e3e8ee;
            border-radius: 18px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.07);
            margin-bottom: 1.2em;
        }

            .about-project-snippet .container {
                padding: 0;
            }

        footer {
            background-color: #333;
            color: #ccc;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 1em 0;
            margin-top: 2em;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            border-radius: 12px 12px 0 0;
            box-shadow: 0 -2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
        }

            footer p {
                margin: 0;
            }

            footer a {
                color: #ffa500;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

                footer a:hover {
                    text-decoration: underline;
                }

        .career-bot-btn-wrapper {
            margin-top: 1.5em;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .top-row[b-acthlapnmh], article[b-acthlapnmh] {
            padding-left: 0 !important;
            padding-right: 0 !important;
        }

        .content {
            padding-top: 1rem;
